10/08/2004
BUCHAREST, Romania -- "Don't Bribe!" is the slogan of a new anti-corruption campaign launched in Romania by Transparency International. 
Aimed primarily at young people, the campaign will be publicised on television and the Internet, as well as at special events to be held in Romanian towns. 
It is being carried out in co-operation with local NGOs and the EU's Phare programme. 
(Rompres - 10/08/04; EU Observer - 09/08/04)
